# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values:

## Flask Configuration
SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key_here_change_this_in_production

## Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:port/dbname
# For Railway: This will be auto-set when you add PostgreSQL plugin

## Stripe (Get these from https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys)
STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY=pk_live_your_public_key_here
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_your_secret_key_here

## Email Notifications (Gmail SMTP)
MAIL_USERNAME=your_email@gmail.com
MAIL_PASSWORD=your_app_password  # Use App Password, not account password

## Flask Environment
FLASK_ENV=production
FLASK_DEBUG=False

## Port (Railway sets this automatically)
PORT=5000
